title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Douglas DC-3 - controlling the RPMs
description:
In this video we will have a look at how you can control the RPM's of the engines in a Douglas DC-3. Those who already did fly with for example other propellor aircrafts in MSFS might already know this but if not this is a short video to show you how you can control them.
